data.description: Beautiful home in the Capri Village section of Grande Dunes across the bridge.  This home is not a stick built home, it's a true Mediterranean home, built with concrete and steel.  This 3 bedroom stucco home features oversized base board and crown moulding everywhere and an amazing park like rear yard that can be viewed through seemless windows in the kitchen and beautiful sliding doors in several rooms along the rear of the home.  This home has a new HVAC system, new paint and carpet and is in move in condition.  The floor plan is very pleasing and includes a huge master suite on the North wing of the home and a split bedroom plan with the additional 2 bedrooms on the opposite side of the home.  Call today to see the lowest priced home in Grande Dunes over the bridge.
